<title>福建会头为什么多是女性</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%A4%B4%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_thumb_wrp&quot; id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;

                &lt;img class=&quot;rich_media_thumb&quot; src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/b2YlTLuGbKDH7RQ40CF7ibv7FK6AbHUefRNSJN4LX0zwvq2aBGyMcUMrfQkPV6IzFt2zfOZRN2Alian9QWWQ9weQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg?imageView2/1/w/600&quot; /&gt;
